        <h1>Adding a Group into the EEB</h1>
        <br>
        <br>
        Here are the steps required to add a new group into the EEB.
        <br>
        <br>
        <center>
            <table border="1" width="80%">
                <tr>
                    <td valign="top">1.</td>
                    <td>
                        Obtain the necessary information to create a ticket from
                        the Service Center foundation data.
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td valign="top">2.</td>
                    <td>
                        Make sure the Alarmpoint group and contact information exists.
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td valign="top">3.</td>
                    <td>
                        Create the data map rule in the Enterprise Event Bus.  <a href="../03-HowTos/DataMap/WebInterface/index.html">Link to How-To</a>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td valign="top">4.</td>
                    <td>
                        Create the throttle rules in the Enterprise Event Bus.  <a href="../03-HowTos/Throttle/WebInterface/index.html">Link to How-To</a>
                        <br>
                        <br>
                        <i>This step is optional.</i>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </center>
